    of 1 of your Digimon that's level 5 or has the [Legend-Arms]\_trait, 1 of your
    opponent's Digimon gains \"[Start of Your Main Phase] This Digimon attacks.\",
    until the end of your opponent's turn.\n[Your Turn] [Once Per Turn] When an effect
    places a digivolution card under this Digimon, this Digimon gains \uFF1CBlocker\uFF1Eand
    \uFF1CReboot\uFF1Euntil the end of your opponent's turn."
